  "short_description": "Turbo Chicken Simulator is an immersive, open-world action RPG. Play as a super-powered chicken in an expansive world. Explore, fight enemies to level up, unlock superpowers, embark on epic quests, drive and customize vehicles, cook, fish, customize your character, and much more!",
