  "detailed_description": "<h1>Add the game to your wishlist</h1><p>If you don't wish to buy the game right now, make sure to add it to your wishlist.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1727537199\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1727537199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1727537199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/c64fd298a2a71d123ad2a28cefad1f0a.poster.avif?t=1727537199\" width=700 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/c64fd298a2a71d123ad2a28cefad1f0a.webm?t=1727537199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/c64fd298a2a71d123ad2a28cefad1f0a.mp4?t=1727537199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Step into the feathers of Cockslav, the fearless chicken with unparalleled superpowers, destined to thwart the sinister plans of the dreaded Foxslav the 69th and his army of cunning foxes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the guardian of the Isle of Cock, Cockslav's mission is clear: To defend his homeland from the clutches of evil, rescue his beloved girlfriend Friendzona, and restore peace to the once serene land.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Along the way, you'll encounter the colorful inhabitants of the Isle of Cock, embarking on numerous epic and hilarious quests that will keep you entertained for hours on end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/b65d279bfd11bf5a0800f8130ad1bb75.poster.avif?t=1727537199\" width=700 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/b65d279bfd11bf5a0800f8130ad1bb75.webm?t=1727537199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/b65d279bfd11bf5a0800f8130ad1bb75.mp4?t=1727537199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Armed with your extraordinary superpowers, you unleash chaos upon your foes by launching explosive eggs from your mighty but. As you engage in epic battles across the vast open world, you'll not only gain invaluable experience but also uncover valuable loot that will aid you in your noble mission.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/d280e097ce4470ed7c23d26b1508073d.poster.avif?t=1727537199\" width=700 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/d280e097ce4470ed7c23d26b1508073d.webm?t=1727537199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/d280e097ce4470ed7c23d26b1508073d.mp4?t=1727537199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>As you navigate the challenges of the game and defeat enemies, you'll earn experience points that allow you to level up. With each new level reached, you'll gain the opportunity to unlock powerful new abilities that enhance Cockslav's capabilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/b5ab51e52e9528daac92c0d0d980a503.poster.avif?t=1727537199\" width=700 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/b5ab51e52e9528daac92c0d0d980a503.webm?t=1727537199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/b5ab51e52e9528daac92c0d0d980a503.mp4?t=1727537199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Own, drive, and upgrade vehicles to traverse the Isle of Cock in style. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your ride to your heart's content by upgrading performance parts and pimp out your vehicle's exterior with a range of cosmetic upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/b193665f285d66fe855b92ff5541fde9.poster.avif?t=1727537199\" width=700 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/b193665f285d66fe855b92ff5541fde9.webm?t=1727537199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/b193665f285d66fe855b92ff5541fde9.mp4?t=1727537199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Explore the Isle of Cock to gather ingredients from forests, fields, and waters. Whether mushrooms, vegetables, or fresh fish, a variety of ingredients await discovery. With gathered ingredients, unleash culinary creativity by cooking meals offering powerful benefits—from health restoration to strength or agility boosts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/64ec053813cab4c0145617fa9eacc738.poster.avif?t=1727537199\" width=700 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/64ec053813cab4c0145617fa9eacc738.webm?t=1727537199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/64ec053813cab4c0145617fa9eacc738.mp4?t=1727537199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>But that's just the beginning of the adventures awaiting you in Turbo Chicken Simulator! Dive into a world brimming with endless possibilities, from trying your luck at the casino to becoming a taxi driver navigating the bustling streets of the Isle of Cock. Customize your character with a plethora of outfits, explore diverse stores offering unique items, and delve into countless other activities that promise to keep you entertained for hours on end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And the excitement doesn't stop there – we're committed to delivering fresh content and new features to enhance your gaming experience.  So, gear up, spread your wings, and get ready for an adventure like no other!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/c64fd298a2a71d123ad2a28cefad1f0a.poster.avif?t=1727537199\" width=700 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/c64fd298a2a71d123ad2a28cefad1f0a.webm?t=1727537199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/c64fd298a2a71d123ad2a28cefad1f0a.mp4?t=1727537199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Step into the feathers of Cockslav, the fearless chicken with unparalleled superpowers, destined to thwart the sinister plans of the dreaded Foxslav the 69th and his army of cunning foxes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the guardian of the Isle of Cock, Cockslav's mission is clear: To defend his homeland from the clutches of evil, rescue his beloved girlfriend Friendzona, and restore peace to the once serene land.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Along the way, you'll encounter the colorful inhabitants of the Isle of Cock, embarking on numerous epic and hilarious quests that will keep you entertained for hours on end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/b65d279bfd11bf5a0800f8130ad1bb75.poster.avif?t=1727537199\" width=700 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/b65d279bfd11bf5a0800f8130ad1bb75.webm?t=1727537199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/b65d279bfd11bf5a0800f8130ad1bb75.mp4?t=1727537199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Armed with your extraordinary superpowers, you unleash chaos upon your foes by launching explosive eggs from your mighty but. As you engage in epic battles across the vast open world, you'll not only gain invaluable experience but also uncover valuable loot that will aid you in your noble mission.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/d280e097ce4470ed7c23d26b1508073d.poster.avif?t=1727537199\" width=700 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/d280e097ce4470ed7c23d26b1508073d.webm?t=1727537199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/d280e097ce4470ed7c23d26b1508073d.mp4?t=1727537199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>As you navigate the challenges of the game and defeat enemies, you'll earn experience points that allow you to level up. With each new level reached, you'll gain the opportunity to unlock powerful new abilities that enhance Cockslav's capabilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/b5ab51e52e9528daac92c0d0d980a503.poster.avif?t=1727537199\" width=700 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/b5ab51e52e9528daac92c0d0d980a503.webm?t=1727537199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/b5ab51e52e9528daac92c0d0d980a503.mp4?t=1727537199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Own, drive, and upgrade vehicles to traverse the Isle of Cock in style. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your ride to your heart's content by upgrading performance parts and pimp out your vehicle's exterior with a range of cosmetic upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/b193665f285d66fe855b92ff5541fde9.poster.avif?t=1727537199\" width=700 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/b193665f285d66fe855b92ff5541fde9.webm?t=1727537199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/b193665f285d66fe855b92ff5541fde9.mp4?t=1727537199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Explore the Isle of Cock to gather ingredients from forests, fields, and waters. Whether mushrooms, vegetables, or fresh fish, a variety of ingredients await discovery. With gathered ingredients, unleash culinary creativity by cooking meals offering powerful benefits—from health restoration to strength or agility boosts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/64ec053813cab4c0145617fa9eacc738.poster.avif?t=1727537199\" width=700 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/64ec053813cab4c0145617fa9eacc738.webm?t=1727537199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569610/extras/64ec053813cab4c0145617fa9eacc738.mp4?t=1727537199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>But that's just the beginning of the adventures awaiting you in Turbo Chicken Simulator! Dive into a world brimming with endless possibilities, from trying your luck at the casino to becoming a taxi driver navigating the bustling streets of the Isle of Cock. Customize your character with a plethora of outfits, explore diverse stores offering unique items, and delve into countless other activities that promise to keep you entertained for hours on end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And the excitement doesn't stop there – we're committed to delivering fresh content and new features to enhance your gaming experience.  So, gear up, spread your wings, and get ready for an adventure like no other!</p>",
